snippet.title: Aethyr - Kickstarter Promo Trailer
snippet.description:
Support the Kickstarter!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1199039590/aethyr#

Aethyr is an Open World 2D Action Adventure game set in a world ruined by an arcane apocalypse inspired by the golden age of RPGs.
